data.description: All offers will be reviewed Saturday at February 3 at 4pm. Home is being sold AS IS.  Welcome home! This Spacious 3 bedroom 2.5 bath Single Family home is located in the lovely Grande View Park Community just minutes from it all!  Enter through the covered front porch perfect for enjoying a beautiful day or summer storm. The Main Level has an Open Living Concept with a large kitchen/dining area perfect for entertaining.  The main level also includes a Mudroom with a washer/ dryer,  Half Bath, and entry to the One Car Garage. The upper level boasts 3 bedrooms, with a substantial Primary Suite with its own full bath and Walk In Closet.  The Basement is fully finished with a bonus room which could be used as a 4th Bedroom or Office Space! The exterior has a great sized composite deck and manageable backyard. NEW Carpet has just been installed on the stairs and landings.  This is a perfect location for commuters with easy access to major routes and Ft. Meade.   The Front porch will be painted in the coming weeks when the temperatures improve. If settlement occurs prior to improved temps, the contractor will honor the work with the new owner.
